      "content": "that makes sense. can u go a bit deeper into the \"cultural preservation\" part? like, if u were building a formal argument for that side, how would u phrase the idea that integration actually harms the social fabric/stability of a group? i want to see if i can find the holes in their logic by seeing how they'd structure a persuasive speech about it.",
